summary:
Requests the Committee to enhance contacts with regional organizations, particularly ECOWAS and the Organization of African Unity, and international organizations like INTERPOL, to improve implementation of measures imposed by paragraph 2 of resolution 1171 (1998);

Requests the Committee to make relevant information publicly available through suitable media, including improved use of information technology;

Requests the Secretary-General to publicize the resolution's provisions and obligations;

Decides to remain actively seized of the matter.
